claim.claim-text:
1. An illumination device to replace a standard incandescent light bulb, including a halogen light bulb, and to provide decorative illumination characteristics, comprising:
a standard light bulb power connector equivalent to the power connector of the standard bulb, which the device replaces, and adapted to fit into at least one standard bulb power source;
at least one light emitter;
driving circuitry electrically connected to the power connector and compact enough to fit into the volume envelope of the standard light bulb, and comprising a solid state circuit which regulates the source voltage and current and provides the voltage and current required by each light emitter; and
a decorative illumination feature; and
an array of one or more lenses, positioned with respect to at least one LED to direct and focus its light in a prescribed way, wherein the lens array is moveable.

4. An improved source of decorative illumination which comprises:
a source of alternating current or direct current electrical power provided though a standard light bulb power socket;
a standard light bulb power connector to mate with the socket;
at least one electrically powered light source such as an incandescent filament, in which the source provides a decorative illumination function in addition to a general, non-decorative illumination function; and
an array of one or more lenses, positioned with respect to at least one LED to direct and focus its light in a prescribed way, wherein the lens array is moveable,
wherein the improvement comprises
a solid state light emitting device as the light source;
driving circuitry electrically connected to the power connector compact enough to fit into the volume envelope of a standard light bulb with said power connector and comprising a solid state circuit which regulates the source voltage and current and provides the voltage and current required by each light emitter;

wherein the decorative illumination function comprises circuitry to control the illumination characteristics.
